<p>
  <span class="nym">Charity</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Middle English</span> <i>charite</i>, <span class="lang">French</span> <i>charité</i>, from <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>caritatem</i> 'charity'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>This virtue name came into use in England in the 2nd half of the 16th century.</p>
  
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">England</span></dt>
<dd>
<dl>
